  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v" sid="JER 28:1" />And it came to pass the same <char style="w" strong="H8141">year</char>, in the <char style="w" strong="H7225">beginning</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H4467">reign</char> of <char style="w" strong="H6667">Zedekiah</char> <char style="w" strong="H4428">king</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3063">Judah</char>, in the <char style="w" strong="H7243">fourth</char> <char style="w" strong="H8141">year</char>, <char style="add">and</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H2549">fifth</char> <char style="w" strong="H2320">month</char>, <char style="add">that</char> <char style="w" strong="H2608">Hananiah</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1121">son</char> of <char style="w" strong="H5809">Azur</char> the <char style="w" strong="H5030">prophet</char>, which <char style="add">was</char> of <char style="w" strong="H1391">Gibeon</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">spake</char> unto me in the <char style="w" strong="H1004">house</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>, in the <char style="w" strong="H5869">presence</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H3548">priests</char> and of all the <char style="w" strong="H5971">people</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">saying</char>, <verse eid="JER 28:1" /><verse number="2" style="v" sid="JER 28:2" />Thus <char style="w" strong="H0559">speaketh</char> the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> of <char style="w" strong="H6635">hosts</char>, the <char style="w" strong="H0430">God</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">saying</char>, I have <char style="w" strong="H7665">broken</char> the <char style="w" strong="H5923">yoke</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H4428">king</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0894">Babylon</char>. <verse eid="JER 28:2" /><verse number="3" style="v" sid="JER 28:3" />Within two <char style="w" strong="H3117">full</char> <char style